           <!---->\n              <!---->\n              <div class=\"w-100 h-y-container h-column__content h-column__v-align flex-basis-100 align-self-lg-start align-self-md-start align-self-start\">\n                <!---->\n                <div data-colibri-id=\"39-c59\" class=\"h-global-transition-all h-heading style-221 style-local-39-c59 position-relative h-element\">\n                  <!---->\n                  <div class=\"h-heading__outer style-221 style-local-39-c59\">\n                    <!---->\n                    <!---->\n                    <h2 class=\"\">Tipos de desarrollo web</h2>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div data-colibri-id=\"39-c35\" class=\"h-row-container gutters-row-lg-2 gutters-row-md-2 gutters-row-2 gutters-row-v-lg-2 gutters-row-v-md-2 gutters-row-v-2 style-212 style-local-39-c35 position-relative\">\n        <!---->\n        <div class=\"h-row justify-content-lg-center justify-content-md-center justify-content-center align-items-lg-stretch align-items-md-stretch align-items-stretch gutters-col-lg-2 gutters-col-md-2 gutters-col-2 gutters-col-v-lg-2 gutters-col-v-md-2 gutters-col-v-2\">\n          <!---->\n          <div class=\"h-column h-column-container d-flex h-col-lg-4 h-col-md-4 h-col-12 style-213-outer style-local-39-c36-outer\">\n            <div data-colibri-id=\"39-c36\" class=\"d-flex h-flex-basis h-column__inner h-px-lg-3 h-px-md-3 h-px-3 v-inner-lg-3 v-inner-md-3 v-inner-3 style-213 style-local-39-c36 position-relative\">\n              <!---->\n              <!---->\n              <div class=\"w-100 h-y-container h-column__content h-column__v-align flex-basis-100 align-self-lg-start align-self-md-start align-self-start\">\n                <!---->\n                <div data-colibri-id=\"39-c37\" class=\"h-global-transition-all h-heading style-214 style-local-39-c37 position-relative h-element\">\n                  <!---->\n                  <div class=\"h-heading__outer style-214 style-local-39-c37\">\n                    <!---->\n                    <!---->\n                    <h5 class=\"\">.1</h5>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div data-colibri-id=\"39-c38\" class=\"h-global-transition-all h-heading style-215 style-local-39-c38 position-relative h-element\">\n                  <!---->\n                  <div class=\"h-heading__outer style-215 style-local-39-c38\">\n                    <!---->\n                    <!---->\n                    <h3 class=\"\">Front End</h3>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n                <div data-colibri-id=\"39-c39\" class=\"h-text h-text-component style-216 style-local-39-c39 position-relative h-element\">\n                  <!---->\n                  <!---->\n                  <div class=\"\">\n                    <p>El desarrollo web front-end es responsable de la apariencia de un sitio web. Esto significa cómo aparecen los colores, el tipo, los iconos y las imágenes. Cada vez más, el desarrollo de front-end tiene que tener en cuenta cómo se ve\n                      un sitio web en todos los dispositivos, desde el escritorio hasta la tableta y el teléfono..</p>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"h-column h-column-container d-flex h-col-lg-4 h-col-md-4 h-col-12 style-213-outer style-local-39-c43-outer\">\n            <div data-colibri-id=\"39-c43\" class=\"d-flex h-flex-basis h-column__inner h-px-lg-3 h-px-md-3 h-px-3 v-inner-lg-3 v-inner-md-3 v-inner-3 style-213 style-local-39-c43 position-relative\">\n              <!---->\n              <!---->\n              <div class=\"w-100 h-y-container h-column__content h-column__v-align flex-basis-100 align-self-lg-start align-self-md-start align-self-start\">\n                <!---->\n                <div data-colibri-id=\"39-c44\"